{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"88ec7249dd","title":"在中央常委会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0ede911ccd","index":0,"year":1937,"month":9,"day":10,"articleId":"88ec7249dd"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji11","name":"毛泽东全集第11卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji11.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji11":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"69ec17549d","type":"paragraph","text":"在中央常委会议上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"88ec7249dd"},{"id":"689e968cd9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年9月10日）有的高级军事干部，对战略问题毫无兴趣，上不联系战略，下不联系红军实际，变成外国教条主义：教学法要研究，旧的考试方法要改变，现在的教学法多是注入式，要注意启发式[1]1937年9月10日，中央召开常委会议。毛泽东就教材和教学法等问题发表意见，强调教学要理论联系实际，军事理论应讲授战略思想、战略原则。这是毛泽东讲话的一部分。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"88ec7249dd"}],"page":{"id":"fbaf676327","publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"88ec7249dd","start":144,"end":144}}}},"__N_SSG":true}